text: This was the first edition of the tournament. Marcelo Demoliner and Nicolás Jarry won the title by defeating Hugo Dellien and Juan Ignacio Londero 6–3, 7–5 in the final. ==Seeds== ==Draw== === Draw=== ==References== * Main Draw Copa San Juan Gobierno - Doubles 2014 Doubles
